	<h2>What each label means</h2>
	<div class="docs-meta-grid">
		<div class="docs-meta-card">
			<StatusPill status="implemented" />
			<div class="docs-meta-value">A route or contract exists, is wired into the product, and should be described as a real current surface.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="docs-meta-card">
			<StatusPill status="partial" />
			<div class="docs-meta-value">The route family or model exists, but the product behavior, data maturity, or contract coverage is still incomplete.</div>
		</div>
		<div class="docs-meta-card">
